  "title": "Where Foxes Lie",
  "description": "\"Rumours spread like a disease. They infect people. They take over.\" Koen fills his days with hockey, partying, and picking on the local preacher's son, Albert. But Albert is not who he seems to be. In the wake of a vicious rumour, the lines between sanity and madness, freedom and control, truth and myth all begin to blur.",
